 CDQ, a Nigerian rapper, has reacted to a viral video that shows Wizkid and Davido hugging in a nightclub. For a long time, the talented celebrities have been ignoring each other on social media. READ ALSO: Peace at least as singers Wizkid and Davido give each other a warm hug at a nightclub in Lagos Davido approached Wizkid in the viral video, and the two hugged and exchanged pleasantries for a long time. CDQ responded to the news on his Instagram page, writing:  “I just woke up now to a video of Wiz and Davido hugging each other. After I have suffered for years trying to balance the relationship between both’. See post below:   A post shared by CDQ (@cdqolowo) 